      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "eyebrow",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Kako realizujemo projekte"
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Oblasti \u003Cem\u003Eexpertize\u003C/em\u003E."
        },
        {
          "alias": "items",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "contentData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "1bcc0f78-4a00-4c7d-979a-2efc66cc18b2",
                "key": "8465a727-27c5-4590-8af1-11e61f532527",
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "title",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Projektovanje"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "text",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Analiziramo potro\u0161nju, optere\u0107enja i energetske obrasce kako bismo projektovali BESS sistem prilago\u0111en realnim potrebama korisnika. Svako re\u0161enje oblikujemo prema kapacitetu, na\u010Dinu kori\u0161\u0107enja energije i dugoro\u010Dnim ciljevima projekta."
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "number",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "1"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "icon",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "f8737d17-b6d4-42d4-8628-0e1615d389e0",
                        "mediaKey": "737f5ce1-52b7-4c91-85a2-396487eaa90a",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "umbracoMediaVectorGraphics",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "1bcc0f78-4a00-4c7d-979a-2efc66cc18b2",
                "key": "88d3c61b-5daa-4324-96de-66248e8af3fd",
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "title",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Integracija"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "text",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Obezbe\u0111ujemo pouzdanu integraciju BESS sistema sa postoje\u0107om elektroenergetskom infrastrukturom, EMS platformama i obnovljivim izvorima energije. Fokus nam je stabilan rad sistema, maksimalna efikasnost i jednostavno upravljanje energijom."
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "number",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "2"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "icon",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "d306bb89-ac57-4432-b77b-185280b784cd",
                        "mediaKey": "090832d7-ddef-47a6-b55d-452393fd43c9",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "umbracoMediaVectorGraphics",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "1bcc0f78-4a00-4c7d-979a-2efc66cc18b2",
                "key": "50ef00a0-ebe2-4cef-8519-3c7157d43ee3",
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "title",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Odr\u017Eavanje"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "text",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Pru\u017Eamo kontinuirani monitoring sistema, tehni\u010Dku podr\u0161ku i optimizaciju performansi tokom celog \u017Eivotnog ciklusa projekta. Kroz preventivno odr\u017Eavanje i brzu reakciju obezbe\u0111ujemo sigurnost, stabilnost i dugoro\u010Dnu pouzdanost sistema."
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "number",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "3"
                  },
